DIGEST
SB 458 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session McMath
Present law authorizes certain local governmental subdivisions to establish local ethics
entities.
Proposed law provides that any tax levied and imposed by a local governmental subdivision
for a local ethics entity may be allocated by the entity to any local agencies under the
jurisdiction of the entity to ensure compliance with state law.
